### **Request Interceptors**
```typescript
// âœ… Add custom headers
ApiService.addRequestInterceptor((config) => {
  config.headers['X-App-Version'] = Constants.expoConfig?.version;
  config.headers['X-Platform'] = Platform.OS;
  return config;
});

